WEBVTT

01:38.240 --> 01:40.520
EPISODE 14

01:45.840 --> 01:48.440
Weiwei, we're back.

01:49.960 --> 01:50.920
Why are you so tired?

01:51.000 --> 01:52.600
You have no idea!

01:52.680 --> 01:54.360
It's close to the finals.

01:54.440 --> 01:58.120
The library is so crowded,
people have to fight for seats.

01:58.240 --> 02:02.160
After studying all day,
my back and my arms all hurt.

02:02.800 --> 02:05.440
It's so nice you get to study in the dorm.

02:05.520 --> 02:08.080
No fighting for seats or crazy crowds.

02:08.600 --> 02:11.600
You all went to the library,
so I got the dorm to myself.

02:12.040 --> 02:14.600
If the bed wasn't such a draw for me,

02:14.680 --> 02:15.600
I'd never go there.

02:16.400 --> 02:17.680
How did your studying go?

02:18.480 --> 02:20.520
I pretty much finished as I planned.

02:20.600 --> 02:21.640
I was quite efficient.

02:27.760 --> 02:29.360
A CHINESE GHOST STORY

02:33.560 --> 02:35.200
Why isn't she here yet?

02:41.560 --> 02:42.440
Here I am!

02:43.680 --> 02:45.560
Mrs. Nai, you're finally here.

02:45.640 --> 02:47.360
We waited until the flowers wilted.

02:48.040 --> 02:50.800
Sorry to keep you waiting.
Here are your rare monsters.

03:04.880 --> 03:08.200
Mrs. Nai,
why is my rare monster male?

03:09.800 --> 03:12.400
Sorry, I didn't notice that detail.

03:15.320 --> 03:18.360
Life is dull. Even my pet is male.

03:19.160 --> 03:20.200
Nai has it so good.

03:20.680 --> 03:22.640
He's attending a banquet in Shanghai,

03:22.720 --> 03:25.200
with wine in hand,
and pretty ladies about.

03:28.400 --> 03:30.640
Don't be mad, Mrs. Nai.

03:30.880 --> 03:32.640
We'll educate him for you.

03:34.760 --> 03:37.440
I'm not mad. I'm very pleased.

03:37.720 --> 03:40.120
Yugong didn't use the wrong idiom
this time.

03:42.200 --> 03:45.880
What? I didn't use any idiom, okay?

03:47.400 --> 03:49.160
I can't ask too much of you.

03:49.240 --> 03:51.320
I'm content
you actually mean what you say.

03:52.280 --> 03:54.160
The thing about idioms

03:54.680 --> 03:58.360
has to do with my childhood trauma.

04:02.120 --> 04:05.600
What's the difference between trauma
and perversion for you?

04:10.560 --> 04:12.920
You've all heard of the idiom,
Yugong moves the mountain, Yugong Yishan?

04:13.360 --> 04:15.800
It's about an old man,
who leads his entire family

04:15.880 --> 04:18.079
to dig away at the mountain,
one day at a time.

04:19.640 --> 04:22.120
I happen to know it. No need to explain.

04:22.200 --> 04:23.600
Great, I'm glad you know it.

04:23.920 --> 04:25.320
My name is Yu Banshan, right?

04:25.400 --> 04:28.000
So I always said "Yugong Banshan" instead.

04:28.080 --> 04:29.360
Because of this idiom,

04:29.440 --> 04:31.680
I was punished numerous times
by my language teacher.

04:36.040 --> 04:38.680
Your trauma is so bland,
compared to me cutting the cheese.

04:42.360 --> 04:43.320
I've known you for so long.

04:43.400 --> 04:45.520
I only now realize, you've had
brain damage since you were young.

04:51.720 --> 04:54.240
I'm nice. I won't say anything.

05:00.120 --> 05:03.080
Mrs. Nai, do you really have
that much trust in Nai?

05:03.480 --> 05:05.600
Shanghai is full of temptations.

05:05.680 --> 05:08.120
The banquet is full of big risks.

05:11.640 --> 05:13.760
Isn't he there for the Fengteng deal?

05:15.560 --> 05:18.000
You know about that, Mrs. Nai?

05:19.040 --> 05:21.080
We had breakfast this morning.

05:22.360 --> 05:23.800
Darn it!

05:24.560 --> 05:25.840
He told you about that?

05:27.200 --> 05:28.240
Let me...

05:30.640 --> 05:34.360
Mrs. Nai, you don't know everything.

05:34.760 --> 05:38.440
Collaboration deal is one thing.
But why is he going to a banquet suddenly?

05:38.520 --> 05:40.560
There's got to be a badger game!

05:45.200 --> 05:46.680
If we get the project,

05:46.760 --> 05:48.840
Nai will have the money to marry.

05:49.560 --> 05:51.320
It costs that much to get married?

05:51.720 --> 05:56.160
He wants to marry
the department belle, okay?

05:58.920 --> 06:02.280
What can you do? Naihe has no ambition.
He doesn't want to marry a rich girl.

06:10.280 --> 06:13.880
It wasn't me!

06:17.680 --> 06:21.360
Sisi, the nuts you bought
this time are so good.

06:21.440 --> 06:23.240
I'll get some online, too.

06:23.600 --> 06:25.760
Just eat, if you want.
Drop the pretense.

06:25.840 --> 06:28.760
You always mooch off
our snacks, don't you?

06:30.280 --> 06:32.920
You know me so well. I'll dig in then.

06:37.480 --> 06:40.720
Weiwei, check out the school forum now!

06:41.280 --> 06:45.400
- What is it?
- Hurry. Look!

06:50.840 --> 06:52.320
What the heck is this?

06:55.760 --> 06:59.280
Explosive! Well-known gifted writer
takes on the gossip beauty.

06:59.680 --> 07:03.240
Exciting! I randomly came across
our school's gifted writer's Weibo

07:03.320 --> 07:05.080
and discovered a new post.

07:05.160 --> 07:06.760
I was only browsing,

07:06.840 --> 07:09.640
but I became more and more excited
as I read.

07:09.720 --> 07:10.760
So I decided to share with you all.

07:14.520 --> 07:16.480
I TEASED C:
THAT'S BECAUSE YOU AREN'T SIZE 34C.

07:17.840 --> 07:19.440
Who's this Ai Chanel?

07:19.880 --> 07:23.760
She's saying Lord Xiao Nai
only likes Weiwei for her body?

07:23.880 --> 07:27.000
She's so narcissistic, too. It's so gross.

07:27.120 --> 07:28.880
You don't know her?

07:28.960 --> 07:32.160
Ai Chanel, a gifted writer
and campus celebrity.

07:32.360 --> 07:36.160
She writes about coffee,
music, perfume, etc.

07:36.240 --> 07:38.360
She's a got a column
in a fashion magazine, too.

07:39.160 --> 07:42.120
What gifted writer?
This is personal attack.

07:52.880 --> 07:55.000
Who is this C, then?

07:55.080 --> 07:57.120
Who else? Didn't you read the comments?

07:57.200 --> 07:58.520
It's got to be Meng Yiran.

08:37.440 --> 08:40.799
If Zhiyi's engine can achieve
global illumination,

08:40.880 --> 08:43.960
our game's visual effects
will improve exponentially.

08:45.440 --> 08:47.360
I'm not well-versed in technical stuff.

08:47.520 --> 08:49.560
Mr. Xiao, can you put it in
layman's terms?

08:51.400 --> 08:53.520
This banquet hall is ablaze with lights,

08:53.600 --> 08:54.920
and President Feng is glistening.

08:55.440 --> 08:56.880
But the light on President Feng

08:56.960 --> 08:58.840
doesn't just come from
the chandelier's light source,

08:58.920 --> 09:01.440
but also the reflection of light
bouncing off of numerous objects.

09:01.640 --> 09:04.800
Our engine can track light rays
reflected by other surfaces,

09:04.880 --> 09:06.960
to simulate a realistic
lighting environment.

09:10.680 --> 09:14.360
President Feng, Mr. Zhao, the CEO
of Era Technology, is looking for you.

09:15.320 --> 09:17.160
- We should head over.
- Okay.

09:17.360 --> 09:18.920
When do you leave Shanghai, Mr. Xiao?

09:19.760 --> 09:20.720
Tomorrow afternoon.

09:21.880 --> 09:23.560
If you're free in the morning,

09:23.640 --> 09:26.400
come by my office and have tea.
No technical talk.

09:27.440 --> 09:28.600
I'd love to.

09:31.800 --> 09:33.320
Remember, Yiran,

09:33.400 --> 09:35.640
be yourself, keep smiling.

09:36.920 --> 09:37.960
Excuse us.

09:54.720 --> 09:57.480
Ai Chanel is likely Meng Yiran's friend.

09:58.400 --> 10:01.120
A woman like her probably thinks
all the men in the world

10:01.200 --> 10:03.200
should flock to admire her and love her.

10:03.280 --> 10:06.560
If they don't, then they're shallow
and don't appreciate inner beauty.

10:08.040 --> 10:10.800
We'll post Weiwei's report card
and shame her!

10:10.880 --> 10:11.720
That's right!

10:13.320 --> 10:16.240
Don't pay her any mind.
I'm not the one making a fool of myself.

10:30.120 --> 10:33.680
Are you angry, Weiwei?

10:34.640 --> 10:36.320
She praised me,
saying I'm gifted and pretty.

10:36.480 --> 10:38.680
- Why should I be angry?
- She's not praising you!

10:38.760 --> 10:40.720
She's calling you brainless, okay?

10:42.800 --> 10:44.320
A nice figure is a gift, too.

10:47.280 --> 10:49.680
What's more, intelligence is something

10:49.760 --> 10:52.120
you can only recognize,
if you're on the same level.

10:54.520 --> 10:57.080
That's harsh, Weiwei.

10:58.000 --> 11:00.720
That's nothing! According to Yugong,

11:00.840 --> 11:03.720
that doesn't even come close
to what Lord Naihe does.

11:07.040 --> 11:11.240
Do you really have 34C, Weiwei?

11:17.400 --> 11:18.560
Let me out!

11:20.600 --> 11:24.400
- No way!
- Let me out!

11:26.160 --> 11:27.400
Who's that in the white dress?

11:27.480 --> 11:29.120
She seems into me.

11:29.320 --> 11:30.480
I'll go chat her up.

11:30.560 --> 11:32.040
Maybe take her out?

11:32.160 --> 11:33.560
Don't do that again.

11:33.640 --> 11:35.480
That last girl is still a hangover.

11:35.560 --> 11:37.200
Don't get in trouble again.

11:37.920 --> 11:42.160
It's Fengteng's banquet. There aren't
random people here. Don't mess around.

11:42.240 --> 11:45.840
You're being overly cautious.
I'm sure she's here to bag a rich guy.

11:46.000 --> 11:47.400
She's no career woman.

11:47.920 --> 11:49.560
Plus, she's here alone.
Who else can she be?

11:53.520 --> 11:54.600
She's coming toward me.

12:11.560 --> 12:13.640
Ms. Meng, your uncle,

12:14.040 --> 12:16.280
Mr. Zhen of Zhenyi Tech,
is looking for you.

12:24.880 --> 12:26.160
Believe in yourself.

12:26.240 --> 12:29.320
Your charm will be enough
to entice Xiao Nai to approach you.

12:31.320 --> 12:34.680
You're right, Chanel. I did it!

12:42.040 --> 12:44.480
So, she's the niece
of Zhenyi Tech's Mr. Zhen.

12:44.560 --> 12:47.440
See? I told you to behave. Let's go.

12:58.760 --> 13:00.600
Your wife bullied me again.

13:06.640 --> 13:07.920
While I'm away,

13:08.000 --> 13:09.440
you seem to be having a good time
with Yugong and the boys.

13:10.120 --> 13:13.280
No. I've been studying hard.

13:13.640 --> 13:16.080
I was only online for a bit,
to give out rare monsters.

13:17.680 --> 13:19.640
Then why do I keep getting
complaint texts?

13:20.800 --> 13:24.880
Complaint? Shouldn't they be praises?

13:25.440 --> 13:27.720
I gave them graduation gifts.

13:28.040 --> 13:29.080
I'll beat them up next time.

13:31.160 --> 13:32.000
Weiwei!

13:33.760 --> 13:35.560
I mean, duel with them.

13:37.480 --> 13:40.240
Stop hanging out with them.
They're a bad influence on you.

13:43.720 --> 13:45.520
You don't need to dirty your hands.

13:46.040 --> 13:47.360
Let them beat up each other.

13:51.240 --> 13:54.160
Aren't you the real bad influence on me?

13:56.040 --> 13:57.440
I'm happy to be an example for you.

14:01.680 --> 14:06.440
Well, time is of the essence.
I should go study.

14:06.920 --> 14:10.240
Take care of yourself out there.
Be careful.

14:10.880 --> 14:12.920
- I will.
- Bye-bye.

14:38.760 --> 14:40.000
Breaking news!

14:40.080 --> 14:42.080
- What now?
- Check the forum!

14:42.800 --> 14:44.600
Is there another explosive post?

14:46.040 --> 14:47.240
I hope the forum gets hacked.

14:50.360 --> 14:54.440
Your prayer is so powerful, Weiwei!

14:54.520 --> 14:56.400
Ai Chanel's Weibo got hacked!

15:01.960 --> 15:03.640
It must be the guys from our department.

15:03.960 --> 15:05.760
So awesome! They've got your back.

15:05.840 --> 15:07.640
SPECIAL GRADE SCHOLARSHIP
BEI WEIWEI, FEMALE

15:07.880 --> 15:08.720
Nice!

15:08.800 --> 15:11.400
That's how computer majors solve problems.

15:11.480 --> 15:13.360
Don't worry, Weiwei.

15:13.520 --> 15:15.840
This will all blow over in a few days.

15:16.160 --> 15:19.000
Did your Lord Xiao Nai do this, Weiwei?

15:20.320 --> 15:24.280
Definitely not.
He never does anything that direct.

15:25.400 --> 15:27.240
Will you please refrain from using

15:27.320 --> 15:29.520
such an idolizing tone when you say that?

15:31.040 --> 15:34.680
By the way, Weiwei,
how did he react to this incident?

15:36.160 --> 15:37.160
I didn't mention it.

15:39.760 --> 15:43.280
You were on the phone for so long,
and you didn't mention it?

15:45.840 --> 15:49.800
I forgot, the moment I answered the phone.
Plus, Lord Xiao Nai is very busy.

15:49.880 --> 15:51.840
Let's not bother him
with such a trivial matter.

15:54.200 --> 15:57.240
If it's not him, who else is so capable?

15:57.320 --> 15:58.600
I just love them to death!

15:59.160 --> 16:02.680
- Lord Xiao Nai is very busy.
- So busy!

16:07.920 --> 16:10.000
My hands are sore.

16:10.080 --> 16:13.000
Sir, here. Is that enough pressure, sir?

16:13.080 --> 16:14.720
Gentler.

16:15.600 --> 16:18.360
- Thirsty.
- Got it.

16:21.080 --> 16:22.000
Here.

16:23.520 --> 16:24.800
How do you feel, sir?

16:25.640 --> 16:26.680
All right.

16:27.360 --> 16:29.920
When Nai comes back,
I'll make him repay me.

16:30.040 --> 16:32.280
Nai's not around, so I had to do it.

16:33.480 --> 16:35.680
How dare they bully
a girl from our department?

16:36.200 --> 16:38.840
Right? How dare they say
Mrs. Nai is brainless?

16:38.920 --> 16:41.480
She's got more scholarship money than me!

16:41.840 --> 16:44.360
The way I see it,
we should keep this from Nai.

16:44.440 --> 16:45.920
He's quite busy in Shanghai.

16:46.000 --> 16:47.960
Plus, this has been dealt with.

16:48.040 --> 16:50.360
Given the news cycle rate at our school,

16:50.520 --> 16:53.120
this will all be forgotten in two days.

17:07.720 --> 17:09.319
You're back, Weiwei!

17:13.160 --> 17:15.040
Is there new gossip on the forum?

17:15.119 --> 17:19.000
No. It's just Lord Xiao Nai
called earlier.

17:19.079 --> 17:20.280
He's back.

17:20.839 --> 17:25.119
When I was on the phone
with Lord Xiao Nai, Weiwei,

17:25.400 --> 17:26.760
I accidentally

17:26.839 --> 17:30.960
revealed the thoughts
I'd buried deep in my heart.

17:32.640 --> 17:33.920
What did you say?

17:37.320 --> 17:41.320
I said, why hasn't he taken us out to eat?

17:47.400 --> 17:48.760
You're shameless!

17:51.560 --> 17:54.640
Oh, no! There's something
even more shameless.

17:58.160 --> 17:59.120
Tell me.

18:00.120 --> 18:02.840
I said, why not make it today?

18:02.920 --> 18:05.400
Since we don't have exams tomorrow,
let's make it today.

18:08.840 --> 18:10.560
Are you recovered from the runs?

18:10.880 --> 18:13.080
- Gluttonous girl!
- No.

18:13.160 --> 18:14.200
It must be my package.

18:14.280 --> 18:15.880
I snatched up a deal online
at ten o'clock yesterday.

18:15.960 --> 18:17.360
The delivery is perfectly timed.

18:17.440 --> 18:19.160
- Hi, is Tian Sisi here?
- That's me.

18:19.240 --> 18:20.480
Here's your package.

18:23.200 --> 18:25.560
- Thank you.
- How much is it?

18:25.640 --> 18:28.120
260. It's a big brand sale.

18:28.200 --> 18:30.440
It's more expensive at a retail shop.

18:30.520 --> 18:33.080
It's 70 percent off online.
A steal, right?

18:33.160 --> 18:34.920
It's not the same dress,

18:35.000 --> 18:38.080
but I think this is prettier
and better quality.

18:38.800 --> 18:42.480
Nice. The style is more conservative
and graceful.

18:42.560 --> 18:46.560
A respectable woman would like it, no?

18:49.040 --> 18:50.240
Is this dress...

18:50.720 --> 18:52.120
That's right. It's for you.

18:52.680 --> 18:54.440
We're no freeloaders.

18:54.800 --> 18:57.160
We have nothing to repay
Lord Xiao Nai for treating us to a meal.

18:57.240 --> 18:58.240
So we got you a dress.

18:59.840 --> 19:01.880
Last time, Xiaoling's beau,
Dazhong, took us out to eat,

19:02.200 --> 19:03.720
we gave them matching pajamas, too.

19:03.800 --> 19:05.560
It's so embarrassing. Drop it already!

19:07.320 --> 19:11.120
It's the end of the term.
Even the landlords are out of grain.

19:11.640 --> 19:14.600
We scraped together what we could
to buy this dress.

19:15.040 --> 19:17.120
So you have to wear it today.

19:18.080 --> 19:19.200
I...

19:34.440 --> 19:38.240
I was just about to call you, Weiwei.

19:38.680 --> 19:41.160
There was traffic.
I'll be back on campus a bit late.

19:42.600 --> 19:46.520
You're still on the road?
What time did you land?

19:46.920 --> 19:47.840
Half past three.

19:51.240 --> 19:54.560
- Then tonight we should just...
- Weiwei,

19:54.960 --> 19:56.960
you should've reminded me of this sooner.

19:57.320 --> 19:58.160
Mr. Xiao,

19:58.720 --> 20:01.480
these are the terms
on intellectual property rights.

20:02.320 --> 20:04.120
- I'll take a look.
- Okay.

20:04.200 --> 20:07.080
Let's talk later. I need to go.

20:08.280 --> 20:09.160
Bye-bye.

20:12.360 --> 20:15.480
Is Lord Xiao Nai upset
that I didn't remind him

20:15.560 --> 20:17.720
to take my roommates out to eat?

20:24.920 --> 20:26.080
Give me the dress.

21:59.120 --> 22:00.520
Where do you want to go?

22:02.920 --> 22:04.560
We're in Lord Xiao Nai's car again.

22:04.640 --> 22:06.520
Lord Xiao Nai's car is extraordinary.

22:06.800 --> 22:08.640
How so?

22:08.920 --> 22:11.360
It's fast yet steady.
Extraordinary, indeed!

22:11.800 --> 22:14.320
Of course! This is a Jeep Cherokee.

22:14.400 --> 22:16.800
It has Selec-Terrain
traction management system.

22:16.880 --> 22:17.760
That's why it's steady.

22:18.680 --> 22:21.760
Salad what? It sounds high-tech!

22:21.840 --> 22:23.160
Figure it out on your own.

22:23.840 --> 22:26.200
Erxi, do you have ulterior motives

22:26.280 --> 22:28.040
for buttering up Lord Xiao Nai?

22:29.080 --> 22:30.280
Hey...

22:32.800 --> 22:36.640
Yes, that French restaurant.

22:38.400 --> 22:39.600
What's that?

22:39.800 --> 22:41.920
That restaurant is having
its grand opening today.

22:42.600 --> 22:43.720
No, I'm not going there.

22:43.800 --> 22:45.800
Anyway, didn't you say
you have strictly Chinese palates?

22:45.880 --> 22:47.040
You don't like Western food.

22:49.000 --> 22:51.400
- Let's go there.
- Right.

22:51.480 --> 22:53.360
It's good to try different cuisines,
Weiwei.

22:54.120 --> 22:56.840
- But--
- Weiwei, good hosts accommodate guests.

23:05.800 --> 23:11.160
That's right, you're hosts
who accommodate us guests. Right?

23:11.240 --> 23:12.600
Did I get that right?

23:13.120 --> 23:15.480
Smart girl. Where's the place?

23:16.320 --> 23:18.400
658 Zhongshan South Road.

23:26.120 --> 23:27.800
It's for you. Chanel number five.

23:30.200 --> 23:31.160
Thanks.

23:31.520 --> 23:34.760
Looks like she doesn't know
what happened on the forum.

23:34.840 --> 23:36.600
My Weibo got hacked anyway,

23:36.680 --> 23:38.400
and the post got deleted.

23:38.480 --> 23:40.480
I don't think anyone would be so clueless

23:40.560 --> 23:41.840
and bring it up with her, right?

23:42.960 --> 23:44.400
I'll pretend it never happened.

23:44.880 --> 23:45.760
That was a miscalculation on my part.

23:46.040 --> 23:48.880
Who was the busybody
that shared my long-form Weibo post?

23:52.680 --> 23:53.640
What happened anyway?

23:54.240 --> 23:56.480
You're amazing, Chanel.

23:56.560 --> 23:57.640
Your predictions came true!

23:58.760 --> 24:01.960
I was being myself. I kept smiling.

24:02.160 --> 24:03.880
Xiao Nai came up and spoke to me!

24:14.760 --> 24:16.800
You should all get out here. I'll go park.

24:19.400 --> 24:20.680
I'll go with you.

24:21.120 --> 24:24.480
Weiwei, one of us has to play host
to the guests.

24:35.880 --> 24:37.360
- Hurry.
- Come on.

24:40.200 --> 24:41.040
Hurry up!

24:47.160 --> 24:48.000
They're there!

24:48.560 --> 24:50.520
We got our money's worth.

24:52.480 --> 24:55.840
Weiwei, look at the table
by the column.

25:20.440 --> 25:24.320
What are they doing here?
Are they dining here, too?

25:28.240 --> 25:31.360
Is Ai Chanel the woman
sitting next to Meng Yiran?

25:31.440 --> 25:32.960
That's probably her.

25:33.040 --> 25:35.480
She looks mean and spiteful.

25:39.040 --> 25:41.080
How did you know they'd be dining here?

25:43.520 --> 25:45.320
I wasn't sure.

25:45.400 --> 25:48.160
I checked out her Weibo,
before it got hacked.

25:48.240 --> 25:50.440
She said this restaurant
is having its grand opening today.

25:50.520 --> 25:53.800
I thought, perhaps she'd be here.
So I gave it a shot.

25:55.480 --> 25:56.840
What are you trying to do?

25:59.040 --> 26:03.360
We already won,
without doing anything, okay?

26:10.160 --> 26:11.800
I don't like this at all.

26:12.040 --> 26:15.600
It's like we're using Lord Xiao Nai
to counterattack and gloat.

26:15.760 --> 26:19.120
And, he doesn't even know
what's happening.

26:19.280 --> 26:22.000
Are you going to desert the ranks,
Weiwei?

26:22.760 --> 26:26.880
Deserting what ranks?
Since when am I on the battlefield?

26:28.120 --> 26:30.880
This is supposed to be
a get-together, but now,

26:30.960 --> 26:32.680
it's not just a simple get-together.

26:36.760 --> 26:39.960
Forget it. Just pretend they don't exist.

26:40.480 --> 26:42.360
We're just dining at the same restaurant.

26:43.800 --> 26:46.880
Once inside, you should eat
instead of speak, hear me?

26:49.440 --> 26:50.600
And don't eat too much!

26:54.400 --> 26:57.400
Mr. Xiao, look at your Weiwei!

27:00.120 --> 27:01.360
That's no way to entertain guests.

27:01.720 --> 27:04.920
After what she said,
we'll be afraid to order anything.

27:05.440 --> 27:08.520
It's okay. Weiwei doesn't manage
my finances yet.

27:09.240 --> 27:11.760
We have to eat up now.

27:11.840 --> 27:13.600
When Weiwei manages his finances,

27:13.680 --> 27:15.880
we'd be lucky to have pickles!

27:16.880 --> 27:17.720
Let's go!

27:31.680 --> 27:34.880
Be patient. Things happen one at a time.

27:34.960 --> 27:36.520
It's because
you took the wrong route before.

27:38.680 --> 27:39.520
Okay.

27:41.080 --> 27:43.560
He rushed over right after he landed.

27:43.640 --> 27:45.840
What was on his mind?

27:46.320 --> 27:49.480
He probably thought
this was just an innocent get-together.

27:49.960 --> 27:52.920
He'd never guess
there was an ulterior motive.

27:55.040 --> 27:55.880
Don't go in there.

28:03.240 --> 28:05.880
That's right. Why should I go in?

28:05.960 --> 28:08.000
Why should I dine for appearance's sake?

28:08.080 --> 28:10.800
Why should I dine just to spite
and torment someone?

28:11.160 --> 28:12.520
It's quality time.

28:12.600 --> 28:15.800
Shouldn't I spend it dining
with him and my friends,

28:15.880 --> 28:18.560
in a peaceful manner?

28:18.720 --> 28:21.280
I don't like this place.
Let's go elsewhere.

28:22.680 --> 28:26.120
- Okay, I'll go get the car.
- Thank you.

28:28.240 --> 28:31.200
If you feel awkward, you can come with me.

28:33.600 --> 28:34.920
Go and hurry back.

28:35.560 --> 28:38.160
One of us has to play host here, right?

28:48.960 --> 28:50.280
You're not angry with me, are you?

28:50.360 --> 28:52.600
No, we don't have to eat here,
if you don't want to.

28:52.680 --> 28:54.800
You're not angry with us
doing all this behind your back.

28:55.320 --> 28:57.800
We've paraded in front of them.
I'm content.

28:58.800 --> 29:01.520
You don't have to pay them any mind,
Weiwei.

29:03.080 --> 29:04.320
I don't.

29:06.320 --> 29:08.240
If this were a Sichuan Boiled Fish place

29:08.320 --> 29:10.120
that I'd planned to dine at,

29:10.360 --> 29:12.000
then I'd still go in there,

29:12.080 --> 29:13.520
even if 10 Ai Chanels were sitting inside.

29:13.800 --> 29:15.680
But this is a French restaurant.

29:15.760 --> 29:17.200
You don't like it, neither do I.

29:17.920 --> 29:19.320
Why should we eat something we don't like,

29:19.400 --> 29:21.440
just to spite her?

29:21.800 --> 29:23.080
It's not worth it at all.

29:23.360 --> 29:27.080
We might get indigestion!
More importantly,

29:27.160 --> 29:30.840
why should we provide Lord Xiao Nai's
pretty face? It's a lousy deal.

29:31.560 --> 29:35.120
Fine, I get it.
You want Sichuan Boiled Fish.

29:36.120 --> 29:37.400
Exactly, that's it.

29:39.080 --> 29:41.200
But leaving like this
feels like unfinished business.

29:43.360 --> 29:47.200
Too much is also bad. Settling off-court
is better than a fistfight.

29:48.240 --> 29:49.560
Listen, Xiaoling...

29:54.360 --> 29:56.040
The best way to deal with

29:56.200 --> 29:58.280
an enemy in the shadows,

29:59.080 --> 30:00.640
is to deny her the chance
to get on the court.

30:08.000 --> 30:09.000
I think,

30:09.600 --> 30:12.240
from what you've told me just now,

30:12.320 --> 30:14.120
our tactics are working.

30:15.240 --> 30:17.640
Xiao Nai is clearly
paying you more attention now.

30:19.240 --> 30:20.640
Actually...

30:22.200 --> 30:23.320
What?

30:24.960 --> 30:28.360
From what I've heard,
Xiao Nai has never dated before.

30:28.440 --> 30:30.560
So it's actually a good thing,

30:30.640 --> 30:32.000
you're not his first girlfriend.

30:33.160 --> 30:35.680
Men have to have some experience,

30:35.760 --> 30:37.680
to know what's best for them.

30:41.200 --> 30:42.400
Is that so?

30:43.120 --> 30:47.160
Of course! How many people marry
their first love?

30:55.560 --> 30:56.800
It's Nana again.

30:59.200 --> 31:01.280
Yiran, don't listen to Ai Chanel.

31:01.880 --> 31:03.320
She's up to no good.

31:03.400 --> 31:05.880
She's only using you
to get attention for herself.

31:19.840 --> 31:20.800
Here's the menu.

31:25.520 --> 31:29.040
I have to get a French cuisine's worth
out of Sichuan Boiled Fish.

31:29.520 --> 31:31.120
What would you like to eat?

31:31.200 --> 31:33.960
Our Sichuan Boiled Fish are made to order.
Very tasty.

31:34.040 --> 31:34.880
What kind of fish do you have?

31:35.120 --> 31:37.080
I recommend northern snakehead today.

31:38.000 --> 31:40.880
Okay, we'll take an eight-jin
northern snakehead.

31:41.320 --> 31:42.920
Sorry, Miss. Our fish aren't that big.

31:43.000 --> 31:44.360
How about two fish of three to four jins?

31:45.680 --> 31:47.440
Should we go with three or four jins?

31:51.400 --> 31:54.800
Come to the restroom with me, Erxi.

31:57.360 --> 32:00.000
You're not in grade school anymore.
Why do I have to go with you?

32:06.480 --> 32:07.600
Erxi,

32:08.040 --> 32:10.960
don't you know you're representing me now?

32:11.440 --> 32:13.760
Do you want Lord Xiao Nai to think
I'm a foodaholic?

32:14.400 --> 32:19.400
But I'm the one ordering.
He'll only think I'm the foodaholic.

32:19.960 --> 32:21.920
Birds of a feather flock together.
Get it?

32:22.080 --> 32:25.240
What if Lord Xiao Nai perceives
the essence through the appearance?

32:25.720 --> 32:29.040
I can't completely give away
my stomach capacity.

32:29.680 --> 32:32.240
What about... 7.5 jins?

32:35.160 --> 32:37.960
Seven point two jins,
that's the bottom-line offer.

32:38.720 --> 32:39.560
Four jins.

32:41.480 --> 32:42.440
Five jins.

32:45.280 --> 32:48.040
Six jins, that's the most I can do.

32:49.720 --> 32:51.680
You're like this,
before you're even married.

32:51.760 --> 32:54.760
Once you're married,
won't we have to settle for congee?

32:55.920 --> 32:57.360
Who's getting married?

32:58.240 --> 32:59.480
I'll be right back.

33:03.720 --> 33:06.480
- You ordered already?
- How many jins?

33:08.680 --> 33:10.360
You're so clumsy.

33:11.920 --> 33:15.080
I mean, don't order too much
Sichuan Boiled Fish.

33:15.360 --> 33:16.720
Six jins, at most.

33:16.800 --> 33:19.840
Our stomachs are tiny.
We can't eat that much.

33:20.760 --> 33:23.960
But we already ordered eight jins.

33:27.880 --> 33:31.640
Oh, no! It'll go to waste,
if we can't finish it.

33:32.200 --> 33:37.240
Lord Xiao Nai also ordered
five jins of Chili Crawfish for us.

33:42.800 --> 33:44.000
That's a lot!

33:44.760 --> 33:47.640
Don't worry. I only ordered it,
after learning of your appetite.

33:52.600 --> 33:54.320
- How so?
- We told him,

33:54.400 --> 33:56.960
last time we ate out,
you cleaned up a plate of chicken wings.

34:06.800 --> 34:09.520
Cramming for the recent exams
burns a lot of calories.

34:12.239 --> 34:13.679
I have faith in your capability.

34:17.040 --> 34:19.280
Who wants your faith in that?

34:19.360 --> 34:21.760
Eight jins of Sichuan Boiled Fish
and five jins of Chili Crawfish?

34:22.120 --> 34:23.120
Do you think we're pigs?

34:30.679 --> 34:33.840
Come on, let's order booze.
We're drinking today.

34:35.880 --> 34:37.920
Lord Xiao Nai is driving,
so he can't drink.

34:38.880 --> 34:42.320
He's driving, so he can't drink,
but you're not driving.

34:42.400 --> 34:43.679
You have to represent.

34:48.920 --> 34:50.159
Cheers!

34:53.880 --> 34:55.239
- So spicy!
- Cheers.

34:57.080 --> 35:01.120
You're drinking too slowly, Weiwei.
Come on.

35:01.720 --> 35:04.640
I can't drink anymore. Thanks.

35:04.720 --> 35:06.840
The crawfish is amazing!

35:18.520 --> 35:19.360
Weiwei?

35:20.840 --> 35:21.880
Yes?

35:23.920 --> 35:25.080
Nothing.

35:25.920 --> 35:28.520
It's so rare to see you like this.

35:28.880 --> 35:31.720
That's why I stopped the car,
so I can drink it in.

35:38.880 --> 35:40.080
What was wrong with the French restaurant?

35:47.480 --> 35:52.120
A couple of days ago,
someone wrote a post on the school forum,

35:53.440 --> 35:55.320
saying that I only have the looks.

35:57.600 --> 35:58.880
Keep going.

36:01.360 --> 36:02.600
That's pretty much it.

36:04.880 --> 36:08.120
They're dining at that restaurant today.

36:08.280 --> 36:13.840
Erxi found out about it.
That's why she chose that place.

36:18.520 --> 36:19.360
Name?

36:23.120 --> 36:24.160
Ai Chanel.

36:25.200 --> 36:26.200
And?

36:28.880 --> 36:32.160
I'm not sure about the others.

36:35.040 --> 36:36.960
Should I say Meng Yiran?

36:37.640 --> 36:39.880
It's only a guess, after all.

36:40.680 --> 36:43.680
If it wasn't her, it'd be slander.

36:43.960 --> 36:46.400
Do as you would be done by.

36:48.880 --> 36:52.080
It's okay. You can read it online.

36:52.400 --> 36:54.640
But don't comment on it, just let it go.

36:55.600 --> 36:57.680
I'm not that hurt.

36:58.080 --> 37:01.840
Ai Chanel was embarrassed enough, anyway.

37:05.880 --> 37:10.280
Let it go? I'm afraid
I'm not that magnanimous.

37:13.720 --> 37:15.200
Are you upset for real?

37:20.680 --> 37:22.480
I'm okay.

37:23.800 --> 37:26.680
It hurt, at first,

37:28.000 --> 37:31.360
but I tried to turn those slights

37:31.640 --> 37:33.320
into motivation.

37:35.440 --> 37:36.720
But now,

37:37.480 --> 37:39.160
those meaningless comments

37:39.400 --> 37:41.560
are no longer important enough
to motivate me.

37:46.280 --> 37:50.040
Now, my motivation... is you...

38:04.080 --> 38:06.280
Don't stay here. Let's go back.

38:16.000 --> 38:17.880
You don't have to drop me off.

38:18.240 --> 38:19.800
I can walk back.

38:19.880 --> 38:22.480
I'll park at my house and walk you home.

38:49.760 --> 38:53.000
We've been walking round and round.
A few more loops,

38:53.400 --> 38:55.120
Sichuan Boiled Fish is all digested.

38:55.200 --> 38:56.840
Let's have dinner with my roommates
after your exams.

38:58.160 --> 38:59.320
What?

39:03.160 --> 39:04.120
Oh.

39:05.800 --> 39:06.800
You don't want to?

39:07.880 --> 39:12.120
No, it's just...

39:13.080 --> 39:16.400
I've felt like the situation
with Lord Xiao Nai

39:16.640 --> 39:18.720
is supposed to be
a prelude to our romance,

39:19.360 --> 39:20.400
but after what my roommates did,

39:21.120 --> 39:22.960
we're suddenly going steady already.

39:23.520 --> 39:25.120
It feels so unreal.

39:25.640 --> 39:27.840
Plus, he's Xiao Nai.

39:30.640 --> 39:33.480
It just feels a bit unreal.

40:07.400 --> 40:08.880
I didn't want to move this fast.

40:11.840 --> 40:13.200
Does it feel real now?

40:47.040 --> 40:48.760
Rumor has it,

40:48.840 --> 40:52.120
a guy ran into Xiao Nai in the dorms.

40:52.200 --> 40:54.480
He rushed up to Xiao Nai and asked,

41:02.960 --> 41:05.560
"What do you think about
the post on the forum?"

41:07.320 --> 41:08.840
"Better to have than be without."

41:15.360 --> 41:16.840
Here's the problem.

41:17.240 --> 41:18.640
What did he mean by that?

41:20.680 --> 41:23.880
These six words don't seem much
at first glance,

41:23.960 --> 41:28.320
but once you think about it,
it's mean and hurtful.

41:28.520 --> 41:32.680
Especially for a girl,
the spite really sinks in.

41:33.120 --> 41:37.560
So what is it that Ai Chanel
and Meng Yiran are without?

41:39.360 --> 41:41.560
As a student of Marxism,

41:41.640 --> 41:44.680
you must learn to perceive the essence
through the appearance.

41:45.280 --> 41:48.480
Ai Chanel attacked Weiwei,

41:48.560 --> 41:51.520
probably because she is lacking
in that regard.

41:51.760 --> 41:54.880
- Can it be true?
- It must be.

41:56.720 --> 42:01.200
Weiwei, how does Lord Xiao Nai know
that you do have it?

42:01.280 --> 42:02.880
Has he hugged you?

42:05.200 --> 42:09.160
You're killing me! My mask is falling off!
All right!

42:09.720 --> 42:11.520
I won't ask about your figure.

42:11.600 --> 42:13.200
But things are what they are now,

42:13.280 --> 42:15.200
you have to tell us if he's hugged you!

42:17.160 --> 42:21.160
I thought about it. I think it best
to leave it a mystery for you.

42:23.440 --> 42:24.280
That's a yes.

44:59.960 --> 45:02.400
Subtitle translation by Lu Yuhan
